          "description": "I had a fracture in my lower left leg in September 2025. I saw many doctors who didn't help me with my fracture as I expected.\nThen I went to CityMD on west 57th street and I was seen by doctor Unana Okaford. And I want to tell you that she is an outstanding, caring, compassionate and straight to the point and very clear in understanding you and very clear in her answer and explanation.\nI strongly recommend everyone to see doctor Okaford when they need help and when they feel that there is  noone to go to for help with their health. She referred me to the right Orthopedist and I started to work immediately after five months of not working.\nIn addition to great doctor Okaford, the people who work there are all excellent. They understand. They respect. And they help.\nThanks a million CityMD west 57th street.",
