          "description": "Have had the most fabulous experiences at the Summit location on 18th St. and have met Dr. Andrew Farber,  an Orthopedist who is nothing short of phenomenal. He and his assistants are always right on time, gracious, friendly, and amazingly helpful. It is a treat to go there and be treated.  I plan to look for other specialty physicians  at the same location.  Peace.",
