          "description": "Dear CityMD Team,\n\nI\u2019m writing to share feedback about my recent visit on 03/18/26.\n\nThis was the first time in 13 years that I had a truly 5-star experience. From the front desk staff to the nurse and the doctor, everything was excellent\u2014professional, efficient, and genuinely caring.\n\nIn contrast, my prior experiences over the past 13 years have unfortunately been consistently disappointing. That\u2019s why this visit stood out so strongly\u2014it was a complete and very welcome change.\n\nI sincerely appreciate the level of care and service I received during this visit, and I hope this standard continues moving forward.\n\nThank you for the improvement.\nOn this location",
